
USAGE:

$f90compiler = Name of your FORTRAN 90 compiler (ifort : Strongly Reccomended)

INSTALLATION:

./install.csh $f90compiler

RUN:

./surfNelcomp.csh -inp  [PDB_filename]
./surfNelcomp.csh -inp  [PDB_filename] target [residue_number-residue_identity]
./surfNelcomp.csh -inp  2HAQ.pdb
./surfNelcomp.csh -inp  2HAQ.pdb target 151-PHE
./surfNelcomp.csh -help (for help)

./refresh.csh (To remove intermediate files for an interrupted or pre-terminated run of surfNelcomp.csh) 
./clean.csh (to reset to the RAW / NASCENT form of the Package) 
If Cleaned, then ensure to run install.csh prior to the next run of surfNelcomp.csh (see USAGE above)


